		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Toronto</placeName> <date>January 10 5624</date></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><addressee>Revd. Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">I have been long silent<lb/> it is true&#44; But now I come again to inform you<lb/> that I am here&#44; I will be able to do something for your<lb/> Occident here please God&#44; I am sure&#44; I will soon write<lb/> to you about your religious books&#44; Please let me<lb/> <del>heare</del> hear from you soon&#44; and if you will publish<lb/> my articles when I will write them according to your<lb/> desire&#63;  I remain dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">your most truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">E. Marcuson</persName></p>
				<p>direct my letters in care of <persName>M. Kassel</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(4)"><placeName>166. Queen Street</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><placeName>Toronto</placeName></p>
